high_descs: Walk around the island and take a right at the dishwasher.
Walk to the stove and pick up the knife that is to the right of the stove.
Turn to the left and walk to the dishwasher.
Cut the potato that is on the counter above the dishwasher.
Turn around to the right and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and place the knife on the top shelf.
Close the refrigerator, turn to the left, and walk back to the counter above the dishwasher where the potato is.
Pick up the potato slice from the potato from the counter.
Turn to the right and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the potato on the shelf, close the refrigerator. Open the refrigerator, remove the potato, close the refrigerator.
Turn to the left and walk back to the dishwasher.
Place the potato on the counter beside the other pieces of potato.
anns.task_desc: Cool a potato slice in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Walk across the room to face the stove.
Pick up the knife on the stove.
Turn left and step forward to face the potato on the counter.
Cut the potato on the counter into slices.
Turn right and cross the room to face the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge.
Turn left and step forward to face the potato on the counter.
Pick up a slice of potato on the counter.
Turn right and cross the room to face the fridge.
Cool the potato slice in the fridge and remove it.
Turn left and step forward to face the potato on the counter.
Place the potato slice on the counter.
anns.task_desc: To cool a potato slice and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn and go to the counter by the stove.
Pick up a knife on the counter by the stove.
Turn and go to the counter by the sink.
Cut a potato on the counter by the sink.
Turn and go to the refrigerator.
Put the knife in the refrigerator.
Turn and go to the counter by the sink.
Pick up a slice of potato on the counter.
Turn and go to the refrigerator.
Chill the slice of potato in the refrigerator.
Turn and go to the counter by the sink.
Put the slice of potato on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of potato on the counter by the sink.
